        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Flickr returns the following XML for empty resultset:\n{code:xml} \n<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"utf-8\" ?>\n<rsp stat=\"ok\">\n<photos page=\"1\" pages=\"0\" perpage=\"10\" total=\"0\" \/>\n<\/rsp>\n{code} \n\nIn Zend_Service_Flickr_ResultSet contructor there is the code:\n{code:title=Zend_Service_Flickr_ResultSet::__construct()|borderStyle=solid}\n...\n$this->totalResultsReturned  = ($page == $pages) ? ($total - ($page - 1) * $perPage) : (int) $perPage;\n...\n{code}\n\ntherefore $page != $pages (attributes of the xml above) and it returns (int)$perPage.\n\nSteps to reproduce:\n{code:title=Steps to reproduce|borderStyle=solid}\n$flickr = new Zend_Service_Flickr(<api_key>);\necho $flickr->tagSearch('kjsdnhgjsdfg')->totalResults();\n{code}\n\noutput is 10, expected 0.\n\nProposed solution:\nIn Zend_Service_Flickr_ResultSet contructor:\n{code:title=Zend_Service_Flickr_ResultSet::__construct()|borderStyle=solid}\n...\n$this->totalResultsReturned  = ($page == $pages || $pages == 0) ? ($total - ($page - 1) * $perPage) : (int) $perPage;\n...\n{code}"
        },
